  How to manage hundreds of Kubernates clusters on production environment
To manage hundreds of kubernates clusters by usinng this installations 1) KOPS 2) KubeADM
Compared to the KubeADM ,Kops is smoothly do the configurations.So,most of the devops engineers are install KOPS on theproduction system
By using KOPS weare doing all the K8's lifecycles
                    1) Installing Cluster
                    2) Upgrading
                    3)Modulations
                    4)Delations
